e6ce85ec094fbc05dd37bd44c240ac4bce30c","tid":277462,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老豆老母本身冇諗住咁快結婚<br />\n點知佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">求其</span>入紙都抽中居屋<br />\n仲要係靚number有得首輪擇樓<br />\n所以為左層樓 佢地迫住去係三日內註冊<br />\n為左註到冊 佢地仲分散去唔同的婚姻註冊署到搶位<br />\n唔怪得之佢地註冊果日著得咁事但<br />\n我媽連妝都冇化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bd3f53b048fc4f9db56618308f5c3f2c79898ed9","tid":277462,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日同媽咪傾傾下往事<br />\n之後媽媽講左句 佢覺得最好彩係細個個陣識左老豆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽到好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想知道下老一輩的愛情故事</blockquote><br />\n樓主講先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知道ge就係 我媽十六七歲就岀黎做嘢<br />\n十七歲個陣係翻工地方定唔知邊道識左爸爸<br />\n之後就拍拖 廿二歲個陣就結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講岀黎好平淡 <br />\n但成日望住兩老坐係廳都有種細水長流的感覺 個心暖一暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話 老母話都唔知點解老豆咁醜樣都會中意佢<br />\n我心諗 你好靚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914d4a2ff5115f80920db8c8e2c69899296f7ac7","tid":277462,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老豆老母本身冇諗住咁快結婚<br />\n點知佢地其入紙都抽中居屋<br />\n仲要係靚number有得首輪擇樓<br />\n所以為左層樓 佢地迫住去係三日內註冊<br />\n為左註到冊 佢地仲分散去唔同的婚姻註冊署到搶位<br />\n唔怪得之佢地註冊果日著得咁事但<br />\n我媽連妝都冇化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個陣拍左幾耐拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626cd8b476fc9b41dea9d5b599ce16ab1981a5e7","tid":277462,"uid":37922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}